{"tid":317419,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★【房屋問題】業界：引入外國「貨櫃屋」可舒緩房屋不足!","createTime":"2017-07-11T12:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T15:08:16.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ba0eedbf5504113efef3dab147684006974bf538","tid":317419,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:16:04.000Z","msg":"香港社會服務聯會業務總監黃健偉今日出席由民建聯舉辦有關房屋問題的圓桌會議時指出，新政府應該參考各項的短期房屋過渡性措施，以解決公屋等候時間太長的問題。他又提出，引入外國的「貨櫃屋」，可以舒緩房屋不足的情況。<br />\n<br />\n黃健偉表示，自己曾於荷蘭考察時發現，貨櫃屋的環境並非常人的印象般惡劣，反而是十分精美，可以成為一種居住的選擇，吸引年輕人。他又指，由於很多發展商買土地後，都會把土地閒置很久，故如能和發展商合作，借用土地來建「過渡屋」，便可以解決輪候公屋時間過長的問題。他強調，這只是短期性的措施，不會對發展商造成負擔。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2017/06/27/010062123.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fnews%2Fsystem%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F010062123.shtml&d=a5uSPgoTmYUyQzUinlWS91zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=e3c9a166\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2017/06/27/010062123.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323e5409e140d6fafc5f64aaebfe35c49e32b7ba","tid":317419,"uid":46155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:16:49.000Z","msg":"哪有地"},{"pid":"eb89674e00e7d2c0bbc26b8e33ef0d0f2b05ca8f","tid":317419,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:16:54.000Z","msg":"pack箱打包<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc633bbaf46b6592be78be9ed3aef2daba41cb55","tid":317419,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:17:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哪有地</blockquote><br /